\title{Triadic Composition}
\pre{\startverb
pijul (-1)  + flox-mcp (0)  + skill-creator (+1) = 0 ✓
Validator     Coordinator     Generator
\stopverb}

\p{Pijul validates patch correctness, flox-mcp coordinates environment, skill-creator generates new skills.}
}

